ssary interdisciplinary cooperation network, and\nto start training the indispensable communication skills at the earliest\npossible phase of education.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Aug 2012 09:26:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-29"}
